parameters.Off: The original voice (no local voice change).

parameters.OldMan: The voice of an old man.

parameters.BabyBoy: The voice of a little boy.

parameters.BabyGirl: The voice of a little girl.

parameters.ZhuBaJie: The voice of Zhu Bajie, a character in Journey to the West who has a voice like that of a growling bear.

parameters.GENERAL_BEAUTY_VOICE_MALE_MAGNETIC: (For male only) A more magnetic voice. Do not use it when the speaker is a female; otherwise, voice distortion occurs.

parameters.GENERAL_BEAUTY_VOICE_FEMALE_FRESH: (For female only) A fresher voice. Do not use it when the speaker is a male; otherwise, voice distortion occurs.

parameters.GENERAL_BEAUTY_VOICE_FEMALE_VITALITY: (For female only) A more vital voice. Do not use it when the speaker is a male; otherwise, voice distortion occurs.
